main event: A civilian observed a moving object that appeared to be a UFO for 105 minutes on August 3, 1965.
interesting points: The observation lasted for 105 minutes., There was no physical evidence or photographs collected., The case was evaluated and deemed to have insufficient data for evaluation., A Form 57A was sent for additional data but not returned., The record mentions a follow-up letter dated August 7, 1968, requesting a UFO report form.
